ssical\nsolution gives the quantum amplitude for weak-field final configurations, up to\nnormalization. Such amplitudes are calculated for weak final scalar fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jul 2004 15:34:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2005 14:41:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
